apiValueDetail.apiDesc:
		 获取或设置将需要表达为热点图的对象转换成热点对象的转换函数.

默认的转换方式如下：
		 private function transformationFunction(o:Object):HeatPoint
		 	{
		       var point:Point = this.map.mapToScreen(new Point2D(o["x"], o["y"]));
		 	var value:Number = 1;
		 	if(o.hasOwnProperty("value"))
		 	{
		 			value = o["value"];
		 	}
		 	return new HeatPoint(point.x, point.y, value);
		 }
